Titolo: Heavy Nova (video game)

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Heavy Nova (ヘビーノバ) is a 1991 video game for the Sega CD/Mega-CD, Sega Mega Drive/Genesis, and X68000 that combines elements of fighting games with platform games and mission elements.  Players assume the role of a robot operator destined to earn the highest operator rank. To do so, the robot – known in the game as a Heavy DOLL – must complete a combat training camp which prompts the 2D Platformer stages. The player then must combat other Heavy DOLLs as the end-level bosses which prompts the 2D fighting elements. A sequel, Black Hole Assault, was released in 1992.